=== Details ===

The '''xAttack''' is a type of battle item. It temporarily boosts the player's Pokémon's Attack by 50% for 30 seconds.

=== Description ===

+50% Bonus to Pokémon's attack

=== Acquisition ===
{{ItemPrice/head‎|Battle items}}
{{ItemPrice|[[Dungeons|Dungeon Drop]]|Random}}
{{ItemPrice|[[Towns_%26_Cities#Kanto_Cities_.26_Towns|Cerulean City]]|600 {{pdollar}}}}
{{ItemPrice|[[Towns_%26_Cities#Kanto_Cities_.26_Towns|Viridian City]]|600 {{pdollar}}}}
|}
|}


== Trivia ==
This xAttack shares the same name and design from the official X Attack from the Pokémon franchise, as well as the same general function. In the official Pokémon games, when X Attack is used it grants the active Pokémon a boost in attack until it is withdrawn.

